@CaptinDeckerSTR I had the Moderna vaccines.
1st jab: very, very sore arm (like Mike Tyson slugged my arm) for one day. 
2nd jab: mildly sore arm & was tired the next day. Took a nice, long nap & was just drowsy the rest of the day.
That's it, but everyone's different.
